---
/**
 * Slide 02 v2 · Mission. Magazine pull-quote, centered, oversized serif.
 */
const id = 'equity-mission';
---

<section id={id} class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-16 bg-white dark:bg-slate-950 vibrant:bg-indigo-950 snap-start">
  <span class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-xs tracking-widest font-mono text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-600 vibrant:text-orange-500">02 / 09</span>

  <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-16 text-center">Mission</p>

  <blockquote class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-indigo-950 dark:text-stone-50 vibrant:text-stone-50 leading-[1.15] mb-12">
      "We envision a world where <em class="not-italic text-orange-500">skill and effort</em>, not money or connections, determine who gets ahead."
    </p>
    <footer class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 vibrant:text-cyan-300">— Reach University</footer>
  </blockquote>

  <div class="mt-24 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="border-l-2 border-cyan-700 dark:border-cyan-500 vibrant:border-orange-500 pl-6">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-4">Who Reach serves</p>
      <p class="font-serif text-lg italic text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-50/85 leading-relaxed">
        Workers already in the building — custodians, bus drivers, aides, paraprofessionals — long overlooked by traditional pathways.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-cyan-700 dark:border-cyan-500 vibrant:border-orange-500 pl-6">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 vibrant:text-orange-500 mb-4">How equity is operationalized</p>
      <p class="font-serif text-lg italic text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 vibrant:text-stone-50/85 leading-relaxed">
        Live seminars at 25:1 student-to-faculty ratio, on-site mentors, one-on-one advisors. Schusterman Family Philanthropies trains representative educators in underserved communities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-20 text-center font-serif italic text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500 vibrant:text-cyan-300/70">
    Featured by CNN, USA Today, and ABC News.
  </p>
</section>
